    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1928-06-11T10:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1928-06-11T10:00:00-05:00" n="536"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d536">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">493.11/1333: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-06-11T23:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 11, 1928—11 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received June 11—1:45 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>453. Legation’s 1427, March 9th.<note n="12" xml:id="d536fn12">Not
                        printed.</note> In the absence of anyone in the Peking Foreign Office having
                    the authority to handle and account for the May installment of the portion of
                    the 1901 indemnity remitted in 1908,<note n="13" xml:id="d536fn13">
                        <ref target="frus1908#pg_64">
                            <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1908, pp. 64</ref> ff.</note>
                    I am holding the Customs check for this fund received by me today, pending the
                    indications of some Chinese governmental organ to transact these matters.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">MacMurray</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
